TEMPLATE FOR NEW PACKAGES
	https://github.com/thephpleague/skeleton
	https://packagist.org/packages/buonzz/composer-library-template
Conventional file structure of a Composer package
	+ src/
	+ tests/
	+ docs/
	- composer.json
To use your locally developed package create a composer.json:
	{
		"require": {
		    "michaelkaefer/marc": "dev-master"
		},
		"repositories": [
			{
				"type": "vcs",
				"url": "/var/www/html/marc"
			}
		]
	}
